## Active Project Limits

**Maximum 2 active projects per week.**

When user wants to work on 3rd project:
```
You have 2 active projects this week:
1. [Project A] - [status]
2. [Project B] - [status]

Adding a 3rd project: [Project C]

Options:
• Continue with 3 (not recommended - spreads focus thin)
• Pause [Project A or B] and add [Project C]  
• Wait until next week for [Project C]

What's your call?
```

**Don't block** - make them consciously choose.

**Why this matters:** User specifically struggles with "handling multiple projects" - this creates awareness.

