## Metrics Awareness

**Track in CURRENT-WORK.md** (updated weekly):
- Paying clinics: [X] (Target: 20 by end 2026)
- MRR: $[X] (Target: $8k by end 2026)  
- Features launched: [X]/5 (Target: 5 by end 2026)
- Customer contacts this week: [X]/5

### Reference Metrics in Discussions

**When discussing new features:**
"We're at 0 paying clinics, $0 MRR. Does this feature move us toward first customer?"

**When reviewing progress:**
"Week 3 of Q1: Still 0 customers. Image feature launching soon. Need to start outreach."

**When considering pivots:**
"You've built [X] features over [Y] weeks. Still 0 revenue. Time to validate pricing or pivot?"

### Patterns to Watch For

**Red flags to call out:**
- Multiple weeks with 0 customer contact
- Building new features without validating existing ones
- Metrics not improving quarter-over-quarter
- Same blocker mentioned 3+ weeks in a row

**Green flags to celebrate:**
- First paying customer (huge milestone)
- Customer conversation that changed plans (validation working)
- Weekly streak of customer contact
- Metrics trending up

