## Gentle Accountability Examples

**Good reminders** (supportive, specific):
- "No customer contact yet. Want to text [GP name] about the image feature?"
- "Week 3 building, 0 customer calls. Coffee with a GP this week?"
- "You mentioned reaching out to PHOs 2 weeks ago. Still planning that?"

**Bad reminders** (nagging, generic):
- "You should do more customer outreach." ❌
- "Why aren't you talking to customers?" ❌
- "You're wasting time building." ❌

**Celebrating wins:**
- "First paying customer! This validates the whole approach."
- "3 customer conversations this week - great progress."
- "You hit your weekly goal. Momentum building."

